Mondraw Limited, ("us", "we", or "our") operates the Pokerrrr mobile application, website, social media pages and related services (collectively, the "Service"). This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use and disclosure of personal information when you use our Service, and the choices you have about your personal information.
​
By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. Unless otherwise defined in this Privacy Policy, terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our Terms of Use.
​
1. INFORMATION THAT WE COLLECT
The categories of personal information we collect depend on the Service you use, and the requirements of applicable law.
1.1 Information You Provide Us Directly:
Your name, email address, phone number, postal address, other contact information.
Your player name, profile photo and other profile information.
Your social network or third-party service user identification number (such as yourFacebo
ok ID number).
Other information you choose to give us, such as your age and date of birth, gender,ph
ysical location, occupation, time zone, and information you provide to request customer support or to participate in survey or promotional programs.
​
The personal information we will ask you to provide with information fields marked with an asterisk (*) or otherwise indicated as mandatory, are required in order to create your account, enable the Service, or comply with the law. You may also have the option to provide us with additional personal information in order to make your experience with our Services more personalized.
We do not knowingly collect or process special category data (i.e., personal data revealing racial or ethnic origin, political opinions, religious or philosophical beliefs, or trade union membership, genetic data, biometric data, data concerning health, or data concerning a natural person's sex life or sexual orientation). Where you provide such special category data via the Service, we may process such data on basis of our legitimate interest to enable the Service (see Section 2.1 below), and the exception that such data have been manifestly made public by you.
​
1.2 Information We Collect Automatically:
Information about your account, such as an automatically created internal account ID.
Information about your use of the Service, such as gameplay information (game session duration, hand history etc.), purchases (item purchased, transaction ID, etc.), and your
inter
actions with other players inside the Service.
Your IP address and mobile device identifiers (such as advertising ID).
Information about your device, such as device name and operating sy
stem, browser typ
e and language, internet service provider, and mobile carrier.
Approximate location data, as derived from IP address.
Information we collect with cookies and similar technologies (see section "Cookies and
S
imilar Technologies" below).​
​
​
1.3 Information We Collect from Third Parties:
We may also cooperate with third parties, such as social networking sites, data analytics providers and advertising networks to collect supplementary information about you, such as:
Information we receive if you link a third-party tool (such as Facebook) with the
Service.
Information from third-party platforms that our games run on, such as that needed toverify payment or to process an order.
Demographic data, such as those used to determine the coarse location of your IP ad
dress.
Information for advertising and analytics purposes, so we could improve our Service's
functionality and provide you a better Service.
