2. HOW DO WE USE YOUR INFORMATION/ON WHAT BASIS?
We use your personal information for a variety of business purposes, as further detailed below.
2.1 To Enable the Service
On basis of your contract with us and/or our legitimate interest to enable the Service, we collect and process necessary information to:
Create your accounts and allow you to play our games and use our Service.
Operate the Service.
Verify and confirm purchases and payments.
Provide and deliver products and services you request.
Send you Service-related communications.​
​
2.2 To Improve the Service and Customize Your Service Experience
To improve our Service, we, on basis of your consent and/or legitimate interest to improve the Service, collect and process necessary information to:
Develop, maintain and update user profiles, game records and hand history.
Develop and improve the Service and user experience.
Manage our relationship with you and seek your feedback on our Service.
Provide in-game (in-app) leaderboard
Provide social features as part of the Service.
Customize your Service experience.
Respond to your requests and provide customer support.
Provide you promotional offers in the Service as well as in other websites and services
(including by email).
Send you related information, such as updates, new products, features, security alerts,
support messages, upgrade opportunities, contests and events of interest.
Enable you to communicate with other players.
​
​
2.3 To Comply with Applicable Law
In accordance with the applicable law, we collect and process necessary information to:
Comply with a legal obligation to which we are subject.
Comply with a request by a competent court or other law enforcement authority.
Enforce our Terms of Use.
Establish, exercise or defense a legal claim.​
​
2.4 To Show Personalized Advertisements
To show you personalized advertisements in the Service as well as in other websites and services (including email), we, on basis of your consent and/or legitimate interest to market the Service, collect and process necessary information to:
Track the content you access in connection with the Service and your online behavior.
Deliver, target and improve our advertising and the Service.
​
​
We may use remarketing/retargeting services provided by Facebook, Google, Snapchat, Twitter, Unity, etc., to advertise on third party platforms to you on basis of information collected upon your access to our Service. We, and our third-party vendors, use cookies and/or advertising identifiers to inform, optimize and serve ads based on your past access to our Service. Depending on the privacy settings on your device, the information collection may initiate immediately when you open our application.
Our use of remarking/retargeting services will always be in compliance with the privacy
settings on your device, and the applicable platform rules. For information on how to opt- out from personalized advertisements, see section "Your Rights and Options" below.
​
2.5 To Keep the Service Safe and Fair
Ensuring a safe, smooth and trusted environment in the Service is a top priority for us. In order to keep the Service and its social features safe and fair, to fight fraud and other illegal activities, we have a legitimate interest to collect and process necessary information to:
Analyze and monitor use of the Service and its social features.
Moderate chats either automatically or manually.
Take action against fraudulent or misbehaving users.
