Depending on the portion of Service you access, your information may be stored on servers controlled by us or our third-party service providers located in a European Economic Area (EEA) country, the United Kingdom, the United States, and/or Taiwan. The aforementioned countries/territories all have different data protection laws, which may differ than those from your jurisdiction.
